connections.

Reproducible as follows (tried on Linux):

1\. Set broker parameters:
imqbrokerd -Dimq.jms.min_threads=100000 -Dimq.jms.max_threads=100000

2\. Create the following resource:
[ConnectionFactory]:
asadmin create-connector-connection-pool --steadypoolsize 10 --maxpoolsize
100000 --raname jmsra --connectiondefinition javax.jms.ConnectionFactory
comp/env/jms/CF001

[ConnectionFactory]:
asadmin create-jms-resource --restype javax.jms.ConnectionFactory --target
server comp/env/jms/CF001

[Destination]:
asadmin create-jms-resource --restype javax.jms.Queue --target server --property
imqDestinationName=QUEUE001 comp/env/jms/QUEUE001

[PhysicalDestination]:
